<li id="cite_note-11"><b><a href="#cite_ref-11" title="">^</a></b> Forder, James. ""Credibility" in Context: Do Central Bankers and Economists Interpret the Term Differently?" (December 2004). <a href="http://www.econjournalwatch.org/pdf/ForderComment1December2004.pdf" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.econjournalwatch.org/pdf/ForderComment1December2004.pdf" rel="nofollow">[1]</a></li>
